Reasoning: The paper deals with the application of deep learning techniques, specifically CNNs, in the field of computer vision for sports, and more specifically, cricket. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of transfer learning, which falls under the sub-category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of deep learning techniques for classification tasks falls under the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the creation of a new dataset, which falls under the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with the analysis of images, which falls under the sub-category cs.MM (Multimedia).
